 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>Harmon</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> 50pp eh? Well try and get anything with HPs on it. Gold Jaded bracers from a jeweler would be cheap and get you some HPs/mana and AC. Get at least cloth in every slot- adds like 12+ AC overall for next to no cost. Hard to advise otherwise for such limited funds. But guess what? You can let pet kill stuff and not get hit! Or at least die in the attempt hehe. For routine leveling (not power gaming) the necromancer might be the class least dependent on gear until higher levels. I forget what level gargs in OOT are, but at level 20ish or so you could head to OOT and camp them for thier eyes- sell for 9ish pp each, check it out.</P><P>Harmon</P><P>Warlock-Wannabe</font></td>
