        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'
 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>thaanatos</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> no one is answering your question, though it is tough to equip anything with that little money, here are some thoughts....</P><P>replace your training dagger with a giant snake fang<BR>travel to mistmoore and ask a high level to stop behind the chapel in the graveyard and pick up the flower there, quick turn in gets you a robe that is better than your starting tunic</P><P>go to Befallen and kill stuff on the top floor for other clothes items...</P><P>for pure cash, go to the orc camp in West Commons and loot deathfist belts, sell them to weekend warriors for 5pp each...I often hit this camp on Thursday and collected bags full of belts, selling as many as 40 on Saturday morning for 5plat each...this financed my early development....you can also hunt in Lavastorm for gems, setting up camp near the najena zone</P><P> </font></td>
