        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'
 nowrap><b><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'>rhys</font></b></td>
        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> My advice is save that money for your spells. They start to get more expensive now, so having a few plat in the bank is handy. When you hit 24 you can be pulling in around 220pp per level at the Brutes in Warslick Woods (good XP), or doing uber-XP and around 120pp per level at the needlite cave in Echo. Either of these places will allow tou to start bying trinkets, and neither of them require any equipment over the basic robe (if you have Luclin then do the needlites - amazingly quick levelling).</P><P>At 29 or so I guess you could pull in cash from the Ancient Crocodile in Guk - I'd say around 600pp per level (selling the gatorscale). </P><P>I know this is more 'where can I make money' rather than 'what should I buy' - but with 50pp saving for spells may be your best bet.</P><P>Nice equipment that can be looted or bought with a few more levels and PP under your belt are:</P><P>Arms: Gatorscale sleeves - the common drop of the aforementioned Ancient Crocodile +4INT +15HP +6AC Focus Effect: Enhancement Haste 1</P><P>Legs: Gatorscale leggings: +7AC +4WIS (hmm...ok) +15HP - or sell it for around 400pp (server dependent)</P><P>Ear: Obsidian Bead Hoop +2AC +3INT +3AGI (50 - 100pp?)</P><P>Wrist: Polished Bone Bracelet: Errmmm +3 WIS +3INT +?AC Focus Effect: DoT enhancement level 1??? (100pp or so)<BR>Wrist: Bracelet of Woven Grass +3INT +12HP +1AC Focus Effect: Spell Haste 1 (I've been farming these at 35 from the Scryer in Guk - No XP, but easy to obtain)</P><P>I can strongly recommend getting  pair of Opal encrusted Steins for a cumulative +50CHA - these are player made and on Antonius Bayle are selling for between 100pp to 150pp each (player made). You WILL make this money back many times over in the savings you make on purchases from merchants, and on the gems, Fine Steel, etc you sell (and thats just at the early levels).</P><P>At 35 I'm now doing a quest for necro +int gloves so those will be free, but if anyone can suggest CHEAP +int/HP/Mana/Resist (whatever) items for Iksar/Necro legs, shoulders then I'm sure that both Kore and I would appreciate it.</P><P>Rhys (Xatan, 33 Iksar Necro, Antonius Bayle)<BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=236573" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=236573</a><BR>All trade, no twink.</font></td>
